title: [Yegharren Plain, Veldt]
description: The distant form of some large creature bounding through the grass moves across the horizon, its species indistinguishable as its fast-moving brownish blur blends with the dirt and grass.  The sea of grass moves in endless waves, blown by the continual breeze from the east.

The distant form of some large creature bounding through the grass moves across the dark horizon, its species indistinguishable as its fast-moving greyish blur blends with the dirt and grass.  The sea of grass moves in endless waves, blown by the continual breeze from the east.
